{"tid":1816011,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"禿頭仲有一年先睇皮膚科醫生","createTime":"2020-01-08T03:04:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-09T02:04:00.000Z","uid":319858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"8a7e0cb1f0fc803177469157f63bdc3b3beac752","tid":1816011,"uid":319858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T03:04:28.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n<br />\n我個頭好似有脫髮問題<br />\n<br />\n雖然我老豆老母話我細個都頭髮少<br />\n<br />\n但最近只要比風吹頭髮好似摩西分紅海咁<br />\n<br />\n剪多少少就會比人笑河童頭 雖然無咁誇張<br />\n<br />\n但係而家照鏡都有見到頭皮反光<br />\n<br />\n同埋仲有髮線後移同頭頂小禿(唔明顯) 頭髮薄<br />\n<br />\n準備入第五第六期脫髮<br />\n<br />\n目前仲有一年時間先到我睇醫生<br />\n<br />\n請問呢一年要點頂先好?<br />\n<br />\n真心需要求助<br />\n<br />\n目前有使用防脫髮洗髮露<br />\n<br />\n睇美容療程好唔好?"},{"pid":"db3392f881b5ffd19fdf8919be0ee57fb65fd5f0","tid":1816011,"uid":38383,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T03:08:09.000Z","msg":"脫髮係冇得救"},{"pid":"96c7c59ab0e7aeaabd77bc2eeb1b70c12604883a","tid":1816011,"uid":290883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T03:09:03.000Z","msg":"試下 保康絲！"},{"pid":"a46141ae21f3feab7b05b210e3800e35640b1126","tid":1816011,"uid":159413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T03:34:42.000Z","msg":"排緊專科？<br />\nbook普通科睇都搞唔掂？"},{"pid":"95046cb28a80863174336991738a67c0b0933c98","tid":1816011,"uid":159413,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a46141ae21f3feab7b05b210e3800e35640b1126","tid":1816011,"uid":159413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T03:34:42.000Z","msg":"排緊專科？<br />\nbook普通科睇都搞唔掂？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T03:35:19.000Z","msg":"我指普通門診"},{"pid":"193e489034ab6ca58bc2197a9ac998faebe11fb3","tid":1816011,"uid":319858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"95046cb28a80863174336991738a67c0b0933c98","tid":1816011,"uid":159413,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a46141ae21f3feab7b05b210e3800e35640b1126","tid":1816011,"uid":159413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1